Morglum <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ugremer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gremer</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 362<br> <font color=#E9D756>(1/8/02 9:13:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2880.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: afk at a 'camp'...?</span><hr size=1> You could also make sure that you put your AFK tag up and that you make an AFK message, sometning like "AFK for 5 minutes, camping the IG's here" so that if they send you a tell, they'll know what's up.  Can't hurt :) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=roark>Roark</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 62<br> <font color=#E9D756>(1/8/02 3:03:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2880.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: afk at a 'camp'...?</span><hr size=1> Ahh, but what do you do at a rare spawn camp if someone's AFK is, &quot;Gone to work, be back later&quot;? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usalenie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Salenie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 149<br> <font color=#E9D756>(1/8/02 3:09:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2880.topic&index=8>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: afk at a 'camp'...?</span><hr size=1> My rule of thumb is 10 minutes.<br>
<br>
Someone LD's out from my group, I hold their position for 10 minutes then start shouting for new members.<br>
<br>
Someone needs to AFK for a bit, if the bit is &lt;10 min. I'll keep them in group, longer than 10 minutes I'll ask them to disband out.<br>
<br>
Likewise, if I get to a camp that is obviously camped but the person is doing his or her wax statute imitation and doesn't have an AFK set/doesn't respond to hail or /tells I'll give it ten minutes before doing anything.  Then I'm as likely to leave as to pull the spawn but 10 minutes has always been agreed with anyone who contests it as a reasonable time to wait.<br>
<br>
